<div type="definition">
<p>FEATURES of TERRITORY.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>There is no concept of a landscape in pre-Buddhist classical Chinese. Shān shuǐ 山水 came to mean "landscape scenery" in Tang times.</p></div>
